    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and strictly garage-kept. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of wear, while the original floor mats and trim appear untouched. Every technological feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist sensors, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of dealership service records and exceptionally low mileage. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
